show.title: Rebirth of the City's Mad Doctor
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/CbQEVP
show.description: When San became addicted to gambling and lost all his money, his daughter's life was at stake. His wife was not able to tolerate the situation, attempted suicide, and died. Heartbroken, San also dies, but only to find out he got another chance to change his destiny. Will his fate change?
